                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-130-victim974 t18310630-130-viclabel701"></join>. On the 18th of June, while I was at dinner, my son said, "Father, there is a man playing with the scale;" I said, "What man?" he said, "There he goes:" I went out and saw the prisoner - I followed him; he left a companion he was with, ran into the road, and threw these scales down - he then ran to a hedge and got through the quick into a field, in which there were seven or eight men: I called Stop thief! and they said, "It is all right, we have him;" I saw an officer. and gave him in charge.</p>
